{"key":"storm_bell","visibility":"public","severity":"high","template":"The storm bell rang. {player} was seen nearby with a terrible expression."}
{"key":"dragon_smoke","visibility":"public","severity":"high","template":"Dragon smoke crossed the forest path. {player} did not laugh after that."}
{"key":"bank_interest_large","visibility":"public","severity":"low","template":"The bank smiled at {player}, which is never free."}
